Package se.js.jesdob.query.condition

Interface Summary
ICondition An ICondition encapsulates some kind of condition, or rule, that is either true or false for a IDob-object.
 

Class Summary
AttrContainsCondition A Condition for checking if a IDob contains a specific attribute, and if this attribute contains a specific value or not.
AttrContainsNotCondition A Condition for checking if a IDob doesn't contains a specific attribute, or if this attribute does not contains a specific value or not.
BiggerOrEqualToCondition A Condition for checking if a IDob contains a specific attribute, and if the value of this attribute is numeric and bigger or equal to a specific value.
BiggerThanCondition A Condition for checking if a IDob contains a specific attribute, and if the value of this attribute is numeric and bigger than a specific value.
EqualsCondition A Condition for checking if an IDob contains a specific attribute, and if the value equals a specific value.
HasAttributeCondition Condition for checking if an IDob contains a specific attribute or not.
HasNotAttributeCondition Condition for checking if an IDob lacks a specific attribute or not.
IsCondition A Condition for checking if an IDob contains a specific boolean attribute that is true.
IsNotCondition A Condition for checking if an IDob lacks a specific boolean attribute that is true.
IsNotNumericCondition Condition for checking if a specific attribute contains a non-numeric value.
IsNumericCondition Condition for checking if a column contains a numeric value, or not.
LesserOrEqualToCondition A Condition for checking if a IDob contains a specific attribute, and if the value of this attribute is numeric and lesser or equal to a specific value.
LesserThanCondition A Condition for checking if a IDob contains a specific attribute, and if the value of this attribute is numeric and lesser than specific value.
NotEqualsCondition A Condition for checking if an IDob lacks a specific attribute, or if the value is not the same as a specific value.
NumericCondition Numeric conditon is an abstract base class for numeric condition, containing reusable function for processing numeric data.
